dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Stephen Long. May I have your name, please?
Hi Stephen, my name is Lori Hughes.
Nice to meet you, Lori. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's two three four one zero.
Thank you, Lori. Next, I'll need your date of birth for security verification purposes.
It's eleven twenty one nineteen eighty-five.
Great, thank you for confirming that. Is there anything specific you'd like to discuss today regarding your policy?
I need to add a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, Lori. I can assist you with that. Thank you for sharing this information. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
No, that's all. Thank you for your help, Stephen.
You're welcome, Lori. If you need further assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
